# <a name="sensitive-information-type-entity-definitions"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-104">Определения типов конфиденциальной информации</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-104">Sensitive information type entity definitions</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-105">Предотвращение потери данных (DLP) в Центре соответствия требованиям включает множество типов конфиденциальной информации, готовых к использованию в политиках защиты от потери данных.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-105">Data loss prevention (DLP) in the Compliance Center includes many sensitive information types that are ready to use in your DLP policies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="06f67-106">В этой статье перечислены все эти типы конфиденциальной информации и показано, что политика DLP ищет при обнаружении каждого типа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-106">This article lists all of these sensitive information types and shows what a DLP policy looks for when it detects each type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="06f67-107">Тип конфиденциальной информации определяется шаблоном, который можно идентифицировать регулярным выражением или функцией.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-107">A sensitive information type is defined by a pattern that can be identified by a regular expression or a function.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="06f67-108">Подтверждающее свидетельство, например ключевые слова и контрольные списки, можно использовать для идентификации типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-108">Corroborative evidence, like keywords and checksums, can be used to identify a sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="06f67-109">Уровень вероятности и расположение слов и знаков также используются в процессе оценки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-109">Confidence level and proximity are also used in the evaluation process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-110">Для типов конфиденциальной информации требуется одна из этих подписок:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-110">Sensitive information types require one of these subscriptions:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-113">Типы конфиденциальной информации используются в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-113">Sensitive information types are used in:</span></span>

- [<span data-ttu-id="06f67-114">Политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-114">Data loss prevention policies</span></span>](data-loss-prevention-policies.md)

- [<span data-ttu-id="06f67-116">Метки хранения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-116">Retention labels</span></span>](retention.md)
- [<span data-ttu-id="06f67-117">Соответствие требованиям к обмену данными</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-117">Communication compliance</span></span>](communication-compliance.md)
- [<span data-ttu-id="06f67-118">Политики автоматического маркировки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-118">Auto-labelling policies</span></span>](apply-sensitivity-label-automatically.md#how-to-configure-auto-labeling-for-office-apps)

## <a name="aba-routing-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-119">Номер маршрутки ABA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-119">ABA routing number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-120">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-120">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-121">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-121">nine digits that may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-122">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-122">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-123">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-123">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-124">четыре цифры, начиная с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-124">four digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-125">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-125">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-126">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-126">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-127">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-127">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-128">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-128">a digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-129">Неформатированные: девять последовательных цифр, начиная с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-129">Unformatted: nine consecutive digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span> 

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-130">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-130">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-131">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-131">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-132">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-132">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-133">Политика имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-133">A policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-134">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-134">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-135">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ABA_Routing.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-135">A keyword from Keyword_ABA_Routing is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-136">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-136">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-137">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-137">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- ABA Routing Number -->
    <Entity id="cb353f78-2b72-4c3c-8827-92ebe4f69fdf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ABA_Routing" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_aba_routing"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-139">Keyword_aba_routing</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-139">Keyword_aba_routing</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-143">abarouting #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-143">abarouting#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-144">abaroutingnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-144">abaroutingnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-145">americanbankassociationrouting #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-145">americanbankassociationrouting#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-147">bankrouting #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-147">bankrouting#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-148">bankroutingnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-148">bankroutingnumber</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-150">no routing</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-150">routing no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-151">номер маршрутной маршрутки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-151">routing number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-152">routing transit number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-152">routing transit number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-153">routing #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-153">routing#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-154">RTN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-154">RTN</span></span>


## <a name="argentina-national-identity-dni-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-155">Номер удостоверения личности (DNI) для Аргентины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-155">Argentina national identity (DNI) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-156">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-156">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-157">Восемь цифр с периодами или без них</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-157">Eight digits with or without periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-158">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-158">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-159">Восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-159">Eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-160">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-160">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-161">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-161">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-162">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-162">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-163">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-163">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-164">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-164">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-165">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-165">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-166">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-166">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-167">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-167">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-168">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-168">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-169">регулярное выражение Regex_argentina_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-169">The regular expression Regex_argentina_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-170">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_argentina_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-170">A keyword from Keyword_argentina_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Argentina National Identity (DNI) Number -->
<Entity id="eefbb00e-8282-433c-8620-8f1da3bffdb2" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_argentina_national_id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_argentina_national_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-182">Номер банковского счета для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-182">Australia bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-183">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-183">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-184">от шести до десяти цифр с номером филиала банковского состояния или без него</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-184">six to ten digits with or without a bank state branch number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-185">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-185">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-186">Номер учетной записи — от 6 до 10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-186">Account number is 6 to 10 digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-187">Номер филиала государственного банка Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-187">Australia bank state branch number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-188">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-188">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-189">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-189">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-190">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-190">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-191">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-191">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-192">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-192">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-193">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-193">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-194">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-194">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-195">Регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-195">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-196">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-196">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-197">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-197">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-198">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-198">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-199">Регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-199">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-200">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-200">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="74a54de9-2a30-4aa0-a8aa-3d9327fc07c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb" />
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
  </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-business-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-216">Номер компании для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-216">Australia business number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="06f67-217">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-217">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-218">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-218">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-219">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-219">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-220">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-220">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-221">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-221">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-222">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-222">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-223">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-223">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-224">11 цифр с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-224">11 digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-225">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-225">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-226">11 цифр с необязательными делегаторами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-226">11 digits with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-227">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-227">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-228">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-228">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-229">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-229">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-230">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-230">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-231">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-231">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-232">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-232">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-233">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-233">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-234">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-234">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-235">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-235">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-236">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-236">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-237">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-237">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-238">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-238">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-239">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_australian_business_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-239">A keyword from Keywords_australian_business_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-240">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-240">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-241">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-241">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Business Number -->
      <Entity id="76e83b3b-01ee-4530-aced-e667a6609f49" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-252">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-252">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-253">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-253">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-254">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-254">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-255">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-255">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-256">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-256">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-257">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-257">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-258">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-258">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-259">девять цифр с делетерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-259">nine digits with delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-260">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-260">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-261">девять цифр с делетерами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-261">nine digits with delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-262">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-262">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-263">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-263">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-264">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-264">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-265">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-265">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-266">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-266">three digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-267">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-267">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-268">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-268">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-269">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-269">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-270">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-270">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-271">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-271">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-272">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Australian_Company_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-272">A keyword from Keyword_Australian_Company_Number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-273">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-273">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-274">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-274">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Company Number -->
      <Entity id="b1fba4f7-7b3e-4bb9-8f9a-9366df604dbb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_australia_company_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-276">Keyword_australia_company_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-276">Keyword_australia_company_number</span></span>

## <a name="australia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-284">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-284">Australia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-285">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-285">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-286">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-286">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-287">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-287">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-288">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-288">nine letters and digits:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-289">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-289">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-290">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-290">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-291">пять цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-291">five digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-292">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-292">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-293">от одной до двух необязательных букв (без чувствительность к буквам);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-293">one to two optional letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-294">от четырех до девяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-294">four to nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-295">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-295">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-296">девять цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-296">nine digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-297">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-297">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-298">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-298">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-299">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-299">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-300">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-300">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-301">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-301">The regular expression Regex_australia_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-302">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-302">A keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-303">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-303">No keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Drivers License Number -->
<Entity id="1cbbc8f5-9216-4392-9eb5-5ac2298d1356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-304">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-304">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-305">Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-305">Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-306">international driving permits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-306">international driving permits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-307">australian automobile association</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-307">australian automobile association</span></span>

## <a name="australia-medical-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-403">Номер медицинской учетной записи для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-403">Australia medical account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-404">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-404">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-405">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-405">10-11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-406">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-406">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-407">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-407">10-11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-408">1-ая цифра находится в диапазоне от 2 до 6</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-408">1st digit is in the range 2-6</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-409">9-ая цифра — это контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-409">9th digit is a check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-410">10-я цифра — это цифра проблемы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-410">10th digit is the issue digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-411">11-я цифра (необязательно) — это индивидуальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-411">11th digit (optional) is the individual number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-412">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-412">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-413">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-413">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-414">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-414">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-415">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-415">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-416">функция Func_australian_medical_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-416">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-417">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-417">A keyword from Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-418">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-418">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
  <!-- Australia Medical Account Number -->
<Entity id="104a99a0-3d3b-4542-a40d-ab0b9e1efe63" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-419">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-419">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_medical_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-420">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-420">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-421">bank account details</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-421">bank account details</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-422">medicare payments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-422">medicare payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-423">mortgage account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-423">mortgage account</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-424">bank payments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-424">bank payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-425">information branch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-425">information branch</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-426">credit card loan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-426">credit card loan</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-427">department of human services</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-427">department of human services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-428">local service</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-428">local service</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-429">1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-429">medicare</span></span>

   
## <a name="australia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-430">Номер паспорта гражданина Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-430">Australia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-431">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-431">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-432">Буква, за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-432">A letter followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-433">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-433">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-434">Буква (без чувствительность к букве), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-434">A letter (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-435">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-435">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-436">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-436">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-437">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-437">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-438">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-438">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-439">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-439">The regular expression Regex_australia_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-440">Находится ключевое слово Keyword_passport или Keyword_australia_passport_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-440">A keyword from Keyword_passport or Keyword_australia_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Passport Number -->
<Entity id="29869db6-602d-4853-ab93-3484f905df50" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_passport_number" />
        </Any>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>   
```

## <a name="australia-tax-file-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-474">Номер налогового файла для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-474">Australia tax file number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-475">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-475">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-476">от восьми до девяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-476">eight to nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-477">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-477">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-478">От восьми до девяти цифр, как правило, представлены пробелами следующим образом:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-478">eight to nine digits typically presented with spaces as follows:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-479">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-479">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-480">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-480">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-481">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-481">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-482">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-482">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-483">две-три цифры, где последняя цифра является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-483">two to three digits where the last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-484">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-484">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-485">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-485">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-486">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-486">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-487">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-487">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-488">функция Func_australian_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-488">The function Func_australian_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-489">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number или Keyword_number_exclusions не найдено;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-489">No keyword from Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number or Keyword_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-490">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-490">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
   <!-- Australia Tax File Number -->
    <Entity id="e29bc95f-ff70-4a37-aa01-04d17360a4c5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_tax_file_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-502">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-502">Austria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-503">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-503">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-504">восемь цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-504">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-505">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-505">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-506">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-506">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-507">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-507">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-508">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-508">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-509">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-509">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-510">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-510">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-511">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-511">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-512">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-512">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="682f18ce-44eb-482b-8198-2bcb96a0761e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-639">Удостоверение личности для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-639">Austria identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="06f67-640">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-640">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-641">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-641">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-642">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-642">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-643">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-643">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-644">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-644">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-645">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-645">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-646">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-646">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-647">24-значное сочетание букв, цифр и специальных символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-647">A 24-character combination of letters, digits, and special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-648">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-648">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-649">24 символа:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-649">24 characters:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="06f67-650">22 буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), цифры, косые черты, косые черты или знаки плюса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-650">22 letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, or plus signs</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-651">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), цифры, косые черты, косая черта, знаки плюс или знаки равного знака</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-651">two letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, plus signs, or equal signs</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-652">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-652">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-653">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-653">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-654">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-654">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-655">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-655">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-656">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-656">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-657">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-657">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
   
```xml
      <!-- Austria Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="5ec06c3b-007e-4820-8343-7ff73b889735" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-658">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-658">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-659">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-659">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-660">идентификациный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-660">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-661">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-661">national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-662">personalausweis repubich österreich</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-662">personalausweis republik österreich</span></span>

## <a name="austria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-663">Номер паспорта гражданина Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-663">Austria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-664">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-664">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-665">Одна буква, за которой следует необязательный пробел и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-665">One letter followed by an optional space and seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-666">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-666">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-667">Сочетание одной буквы, семи цифр и одного пробела:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-667">A combination of one letter, seven digits, and one space:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-668">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-668">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-669">одно пространство (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-669">one space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-670">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-670">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-671">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-671">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-672">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-672">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-673">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-673">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-674">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-674">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-675">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-675">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-676">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-676">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-677">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_eu_passport_date1` ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-677">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-678">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-678">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-679">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-679">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-680">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-680">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1c96ae4e-303b-447d-86c7-77113ac266bf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-social-security-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-701">Номер социального обеспечения для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-701">Austria social security number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-702">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-702">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-703">10 цифр в указанном формате</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-703">10 digits in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-704">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-704">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-705">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-705">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-706">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-706">three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-707">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-707">one check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-708">шесть цифр, соответствующие дате рождения (ДДММАЙ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-708">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-709">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-709">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-710">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-710">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-711">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-711">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-712">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-712">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-713">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-713">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-714">находится ключевое  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово из.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-714">a keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="06f67-715">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-715">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-716">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-716">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Social Security Number -->
      <Entity id="6896a906-86c9-4d19-a2da-6e43ccd19b7b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-742">Идентификационный номер налога для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-742">Austria tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-743">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-743">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-744">девять цифр с необязательным дефишем и косой чертой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-744">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-745">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-745">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-746">девять цифр с необязательным дефишем и косой чертой:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-746">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-747">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-747">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-748">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-748">a hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-749">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-749">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-750">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-750">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-751">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-751">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-752">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-752">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-753">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-753">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-754">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-754">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-755">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-755">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-756">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-756">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-757">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-757">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="06f67-758">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-758">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-759">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-759">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="4fd58d22-af28-4451-b18a-6f722430a56d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-value-added-tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-782">Налог на добавленную стоимость для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-782">Austria value added tax</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="06f67-783">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-783">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-784">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-784">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-785">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-785">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-786">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-786">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-787">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-787">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-788">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-788">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-789">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-789">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-790">11-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-790">11-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-791">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-791">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-792">11-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-792">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-793">A или a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-793">A or a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-794">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-794">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-795">Дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-795">Optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-796">U или u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-796">U or u</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-797">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-797">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-798">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-798">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-799">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-799">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-800">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-800">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-801">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-801">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-802">одна или две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-802">one or two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-803">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-803">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-804">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-804">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-805">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-805">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-806">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-806">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-807">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-807">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-808">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-808">A keyword from Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-809">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-809">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-810">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-810">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="b6a3eda2-c56c-4b69-a5f7-dca34db00f48" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-811">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-811">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_austria_value_added_tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-812">Keyword_austria_value_added_tax</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-812">Keyword_austria_value_added_tax</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-815">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-815">austrian vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-816">vat no.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-816">vat no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-817">vatno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-817">vatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-818">номер налога на добавленную стоимость</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-818">value added tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-819">vat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-819">austrian vat</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-820">mwst</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-820">mwst</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-821">umsatzsteuernummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-821">umsatzsteuernummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-822">mwstnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-822">mwstnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-823">ust.-identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-823">ust.-identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-824">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-824">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-825">идентификационный номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-825">vat identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-826">atu number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-826">atu number</span></span>
