## <a name="ireland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6180">Номер паспорта гражданина Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6180">Ireland passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6181">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6181">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6182">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6182">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6183">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6183">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6184">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6184">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6185">Две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6185">Two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6186">семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6186">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6187">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6187">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6188">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6188">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6189">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6189">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6190">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6190">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6191">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6191">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6192">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6192">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6193">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM ГГ ГГ (пример — 01 BEA/MAY 1988) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6193">The regular expression `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 BEA/MAY 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6194">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6194">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6195">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6195">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6196">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6196">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="a2130f27-9ee2-4103-84f9-a6b1ee7d0cbf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-personal-public-service-pps-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6220">Номер личной службы (PPS) для Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6220">Ireland personal public service (PPS) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6221">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6221">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6222">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012 г.):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6222">Old format (until 31 December 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6223">семь цифр, за которыми следуют 1–2 буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6223">seven digits followed by 1-2 letters</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6224">Новый формат (1 января 2013 г. и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6224">New format (1 January 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6225">семь цифр, за которыми следуют две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6225">seven digits followed by two letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6226">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6226">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6227">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012 г.):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6227">Old format (until 31 December 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6228">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6228">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6229">от одной до двух букв (без чувствительность к буквам);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6229">one to two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6230">Новый формат (1 января 2013 г. и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6230">New format (1 January 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6231">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6231">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6232">буква (без регистрации буквы), которая является алфавитной провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6232">a letter (not case-sensitive) which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6233">Необязательная буква в диапазоне A-I или W</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6233">An optional letter in the range A-I, or “W”</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6234">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6234">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6235">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6235">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6236">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6236">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6237">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6237">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6238">функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6238">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6239">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6239">A keyword from Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6240">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6240">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6241">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6241">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6242">функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6242">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6243">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6243">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ireland Personal Public Service (PPS) Number -->
      <Entity id="1cdb674d-c19a-4fcf-9f4b-7f56cc87345a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6252">pps no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6252">pps no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6253">PPS-номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6253">pps number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6254">pps num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6254">pps num</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6255">PPS service no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6255">pps service no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6256">ppsn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6256">ppsn</span></span>

## <a name="israel-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6288">Номер банковского счета для Израиль</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6288">Israel bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6289">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6289">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6290">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6290">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6291">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6291">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6292">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6292">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6293">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6293">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6294">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6294">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6295">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6295">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6296">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6296">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6297">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6297">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6298">Неформатированные:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6298">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6299">	13 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6299">13 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6300">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6300">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6301">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6301">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6302">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6302">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6303">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6303">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6304">регулярное выражение Regex_israel_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6304">The regular expression Regex_israel_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6305">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_israel_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6305">A keyword from Keyword_israel_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="7d08b2ff-a0b9-437f-957c-aeddbf9b2b25" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_israel_bank_account_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_israel_bank_account_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6306">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6306">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6307">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6307">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6308">Bank Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6308">Bank Account Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6310">Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6310">Account Number</span></span>

## <a name="israel-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6312">Национальный идентификационный номер для Израиля</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6312">Israel national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6313">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6313">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6314">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6314">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6315">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6315">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6316">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6316">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6317">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6317">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6318">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6318">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6319">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6319">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6320">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6320">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6321">функция Func_israeli_national_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6321">The function Func_israeli_national_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6322">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Israel_National_ID;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6322">A keyword from Keyword_Israel_National_ID is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6323">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6323">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel National ID Number -->
<Entity id="e05881f5-1db1-418c-89aa-a3ac5c5277ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_israeli_national_id_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Israel_National_ID" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

-   <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6330">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6330">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span></span>

## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6342">Номер водительского удостоверения для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6342">Italy driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6343">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера водительского удостоверения ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6343">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6344">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6344">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6345">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6345">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6346">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6346">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6347">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6347">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6348">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6348">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6349">буква "A" или "V" (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6349">the letter "A" or "V" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6350">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6350">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6351">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6351">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6352">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6352">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6353">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6353">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6354">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6354">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6355">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6355">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6356">регулярное выражение Regex_italy_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6356">The regular expression Regex_italy_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6357">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6357">A keyword from Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
<Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6366">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6366">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6367">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6367">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6368">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6368">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6369">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6369">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6370">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6370">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6371">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6371">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6372">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6372">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6373">16-значное сочетание букв и цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6373">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6374">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6374">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6375">16-значное сочетание букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6375">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6376">три буквы, соответствующие первым трем consonants в имени семейства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6376">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6377">три буквы, соответствующие первому, третьему и четвертому consonants в первом имени</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6377">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6378">две цифры, соответствующие последним цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6378">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6379">одна буква, соответствующая букве месяца рождения, — буквы используются в алфавитном порядке, но используются только буквы A к E, H, L, M, P, R to T (таким образом, январь A, а октябрь — R)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6379">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (so, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6380">две цифры, соответствующие дню месяца рождения, чтобы различать полы, 40 добавляется в день рождения для</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6380">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth—in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6381">четыре цифры, соответствующие коду региона, определенному для страны, где был человек ( коды для внешних стран)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6381">four digits that correspond to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6382">одна цифра четности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6382">one parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6383">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6383">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6384">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6384">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6385">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6385">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6386">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6386">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6387">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6387">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6388">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6388">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6389">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6389">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6390">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6390">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6425">Номер паспорта гражданина Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6425">Italy passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6426">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6426">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6427">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6427">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6428">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6428">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6429">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6429">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6430">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6430">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6431">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6431">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6432">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6432">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6433">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6433">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6434">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6434">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6435">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6435">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6436">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6436">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6437">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6437">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6438">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM ГГ ГГ (пример — 01 GEN/JAN 1988) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6438">The regular expression `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 GEN/JAN 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6439">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6439">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6440">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6440">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6441">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6441">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="39811019-4750-445f-b26d-4c0e6c431544" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6464">дата окончания срока действия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6464">date of expiry</span></span>


## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6465">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6465">Italy value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6466">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6466">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6467">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6467">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6468">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6468">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6469">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6469">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6470">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6470">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6471">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6471">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6472">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6472">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6473">13-символьный буквонумерный шаблон с необязательными делетерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6473">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6474">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6474">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6475">13 символов букв и цифр с необязательными разнородных символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6475">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6476">I или i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6476">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6477">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6477">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6478">необязательное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6478">optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6479">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6479">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6480">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6480">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6481">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6481">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6482">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6482">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6483">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6483">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6484">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6484">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6485">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6485">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6486">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6486">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6487">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6487">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6488">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6488">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6489">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6489">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6490">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6490">vat number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6492">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6492">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6493">iva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6493">iva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6494">iva #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6494">iva#</span></span>


## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6495">Номер банковского счета для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6495">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6496">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6496">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6497">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6497">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6498">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6498">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6499">номер банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6499">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6500">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6500">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6501">код филиала банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6501">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6502">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6502">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6503">пробел или тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6503">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6504">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6504">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6505">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6505">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6506">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6506">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6507">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6507">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6508">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6508">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6509">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6509">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6510">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6510">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6511">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6511">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6512">функция Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6512">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6513">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6513">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6514">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6514">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6515">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6515">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6516">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6516">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6563">Номер водительского удостоверения для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6563">Japan driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6564">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6564">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6565">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6565">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6566">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6566">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6567">12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6567">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6568">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6568">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6569">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6569">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6570">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6570">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6571">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6571">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6572">функция Func_jp_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6572">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6573">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6573">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6611">Мой номер для Японии — корпоративный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6611">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6612">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6612">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6613">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6613">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6614">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6614">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6615">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6615">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6616">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6616">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6617">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6617">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6618">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6618">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6619">13-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6619">13-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6620">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6620">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6621">13-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6621">13-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6622">одна цифра от одной до девяти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6622">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6623">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6623">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6624">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6624">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6625">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6625">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6626">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6626">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6627">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6627">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6628">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6628">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6629">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6629">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6630">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6630">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6631">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6631">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6647">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6647">communication compliance policies</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6650">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6650">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6651">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6651">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6654">12-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6654">12-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6655">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6655">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6656">дополнительное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6656">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6657">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6657">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6658">дополнительное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6658">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6659">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6659">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6660">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6660">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6661">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6661">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6662">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6662">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6663">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6663">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6664">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6664">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6665">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6665">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6666">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6666">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6667">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6667">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6678">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6678">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>

## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6680">Номер паспорта гражданина Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6680">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6681">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6681">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6682">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6682">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6683">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6683">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6684">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6684">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6685">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6685">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6686">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6686">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6687">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6687">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6688">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6688">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6689">функция Func_jp_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6689">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6690">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6690">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6695">Passport No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6695">Passport No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6696">Passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6696">Passport #</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6699">パスポートナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6699">パスポートナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6700">パスポート＃</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6700">パスポート＃</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6701">パスポート #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6701">パスポート#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6702">パポ>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6702">パスポートNo.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6705">旅券番号♯</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6705">旅券番号♯</span></span>

## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6707">Номер карты для проживания в Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6707">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6708">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6708">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6709">12 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6709">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6710">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6710">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6711">12 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6711">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6712">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6712">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6713">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6713">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6714">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6714">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6715">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6715">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6716">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6716">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6717">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6717">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6718">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6718">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6719">Регулярное выражение Regex_jp_residence_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6719">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6720">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_residence_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6720">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6721">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6721">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6722">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6722">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6723">Номер карты для проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6723">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6724">Карты проживания нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6724">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6725">Карточка для проживания #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6725">Residence card #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6726">在留カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6726">在留カード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6727">在留カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6727">在留カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6728">在留番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6728">在留番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6729">Номер регистрации резидента Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6729">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6730">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6730">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6731">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6731">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6732">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6732">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6733">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6733">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6734">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6734">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6735">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6735">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6736">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6736">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6737">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6737">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6738">функция Func_jp_resident_registration_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6738">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6739">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6739">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6740">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6740">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_resident_registration_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6741">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6741">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6742">Resident Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6742">Resident Registration Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6743">Residents Basic Registry Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6743">Residents Basic Registry Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6744">Resident Registration No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6744">Resident Registration No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6745">Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6745">Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6746">Residents Basic Registry No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6746">Residents Basic Registry No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6747">Basic Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6747">Basic Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6748">外国人登録証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6748">外国人登録証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6749">証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6749">証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6750">登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6750">登録番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6751">外国人登録証</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6751">外国人登録証</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6752">Номер социального страхования для Японии (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6752">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6753">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6753">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6754">7–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6754">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6755">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6755">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6756">7–12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6756">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6757">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6757">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6758">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6758">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6759">шесть цифр ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6759">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6760">7–12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6760">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6761">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6761">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6762">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6762">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6763">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6763">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6764">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6764">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6765">функция Func_jp_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6765">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6766">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6766">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6767">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6767">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6768">функция Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6768">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6769">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6769">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6770">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6770">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6771">Keyword_jp_sin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6771">Keyword_jp_sin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6772">Social Insurance No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6772">Social Insurance No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6773">Social Insurance Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6773">Social Insurance Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6774">Social Insurance Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6774">Social Insurance Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6775">健康保険被保険者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6775">健康保険被保険者番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6776">健保番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6776">健保番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6777">基礎年金番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6777">基礎年金番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6778">雇用保険被保険者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6778">雇用保険被保険者番号</span></span>

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6790">Номер водительского удостоверения для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6790">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6791">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6791">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6792">три буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6792">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6793">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6793">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6794">три буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6794">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6795">три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6795">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6796">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6796">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6797">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6797">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6798">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6798">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="06f67-6799">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6799">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="06f67-6800">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6800">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6801">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6801">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="06f67-6802">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="06f67-6802">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
